**Workflow:**
User -> Planner;
Planner -> FileAnalyzer;
FileAnalyzer -> Summarizer;
Summarizer -> End.

**Description:**
First, the Planner analyzes the user's query and creates a plan for the FileAnalyzer to extract employee profiles and gift details from the document. Next, the FileAnalyzer executes this plan to gather structured data. Finally, the Summarizer processes this data to deduce which employee's gift was missing (based on unmet recipient interests) and identifies the corresponding giver.
